<h3 id="toc14"><span style="font-family: Dearest;"><span>Day 6; (Tuesday/Wednesday)</span></span></h3>
<h3 id="toc15"><span><sup>Evening (Auditions):</sup></span></h3>
<p>Wish me luck.</p>
<h3 id="toc16"><span><sup>Morning (<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">____________________</span>):</sup></span></h3>
<p>To be written.<br /></p>
